&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;</summary>
		<content type="html">&lt;h4&gt;Boas Práticas com Bancos de Dados&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Boas práticas em SQL para desenvolvedores&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jmmwrite.wordpress.com/2007/12/19/boas-praticas-em-sql-para-desenvolvedores/&quot;&gt;https://jmmwrite.wordpress.com/2007/12/19/boas-praticas-em-sql-para-desenvolvedores/&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Práticas Recomendadas - Mauro Pichiliani&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://imasters.com.br/artigo/266/sql-server/praticas-recomendadas/?trace=1519021197&amp;amp;source=single&quot;&gt;https://imasters.com.br/artigo/266/sql-server/praticas-recomendadas/?trace=1519021197&amp;amp;source=single&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Documentação do DBA&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://imasters.com.br/artigo/6392/sql-server/documentacao-do-dba/?trace=1519021197&amp;amp;source=single&quot;&gt;https://imasters.com.br/artigo/6392/sql-server/documentacao-do-dba/?trace=1519021197&amp;amp;source=single&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

